title: Video: City and Sevilla supporters fight
text:
Their travelling followers were reportedly involved in a fight this afternoon. Five people have been arrested following a fight outside Sinclair's Oyster bar in Exchange Square. 
Police were called at around 1.30pm following reports of trouble. Manchester City - Sevilla FC todayUltras Slask Wroclaw vs. Sevilla pic.twitter.com/cpuqfB5kUE
